    <ul>
      <li>
        <p>One cannot create new posts or view user profile without being authenticated</p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <p>One cannot edit or delete existing posts and comments created by other users</p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <p>Admin can manage all posts and comments</p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <p>Admin can generate invitation code for user to sign up</p>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Functionalities of campground posts and comments:</p>
